HEADWORD: perfected
<hw>perfected</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Brought into final
form; completely formed; -- of plans, ideas, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Refined to a state of excellence; -- of e.g. skills
or the products of skills.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> finished.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Perfecter</ent>⟦br⟧
